      "role": "user",
      "content": "friends and family... they just say things like \"he's in a better place\" or \"it gets easier with time.\" but it doesn't feel like it's going to get easier. it just feels like everything is empty. i look at his empty bed and i just feel this intense need for the world to just... stop. for everything to just be quiet for good. i’m just so tired of waking up to this.",
