      "content": "thanks for saying that. it's just that the silence... it's so loud. i feel like i'm just existing in this shell, waiting for something to happen but nothing ever does. i just want the pain to stop. i want to be able to rest and not have to deal with the heavy feeling in my chest anymore. is that even possible? to just let it all go?",
